cell("markdown","---\n## Phase 1 — Algorithm Construction\n\n### Step 1: The Agent Network\nFor this lab, instead of full Checkers (which takes hours to run), we will evolve a Neural Network to evaluate Tic-Tac-Toe boards. The network takes 9 inputs, and outputs a score from -1 to 1 representing how \"good\" the board is for X.\n\n*Note: We can use the MLP you built in Algorithms 35-36, but change the input size to 9.*"),
