cell("markdown","# Algorithms 43: Convolutional Blondie24\n\n**Learning Objectives:**\n1. Understand the spatial limits of standard MLPs\n2. Design a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) architecture\n3. Re-implement the Convolutional layer of Blondie24\n\n**Prerequisites:** Algorithms 40-42\n**Estimated time:** 60 minutes\n**Textbook:** *Justin Skycak — Intro to Algorithms & Machine Learning* Chapter 43"),
